import React from 'react';
import { Grid } from '@mui/material';

const Home = () => {
    return (
        <>
           <Grid container spacing={4} justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" sx={{height:"100%"}}>
  
       <Grid xs={12} sx={{bgcolor:"#000000",height:"10%"}}>
     Profile
       </Grid>
       <Grid xs={3} sx={{bgcolor:"#000000",color:"#ffffff"}}>
     Message Center
       </Grid>
       <Grid xs={3} sx={{bgcolor:"#000000",ml:1,color:"#ffffff"}}>
     Files
       </Grid>
       <Grid xs={3} sx={{bgcolor:"#000000",ml:1,color:"#ffffff"}}>
     Order Details
       </Grid>
           </Grid>
        </>
    )
}

export default Home
